OL,4,CDriver sacked for drinking in club
OL,5,Cwhile sick wins tribunal
OL,6, A driver who was sacked after he was
OL,7, seen drinking in a social club while
OL,8, off work through illness has won his
OL,9, case at an employment tribunal.
OL,11,FColin Kane, 66, was fired by Debmat
OL,12,FSurfacing in Ryton, Gateshead, after he
OL,13,Fwas seen smoking outside a bar in March
OL,14,F2020.
OL,16,FMr Kane, who has chronic obstructive
OL,17,Fpulmonary disease, was found not to
OL,18,Fhave broken the company's rules.
OL,20,FJudge Andrea Pitt ruled that Mr Kane
OL,21,Fhad been unfairly dismissed.
